Package sudoku.cs

Interface Summary
Client Remote interface for the Sudoku Client.
Player Represents a Sudoku player.
Server Remote interface for the Sudoku Server.
 

Class Summary
ClientCallback Starts a thread that will send messages to the clients.
ClientModel Implements the Client interface and models a game of Sudoku.
ComputerPlayer Represents a computer-controlled Sudoku player.
Dictionary A searchable dictionary of words suitable for Sudoku playing.
EndGameAll Sends a message to the Clients to end the game.
HumanPlayer Represents a "REAL" Sudoku player.
PauseAll Sends a message to the Clients to pause the game.
PlayerChangedTellAll Sends a message to the Clients that a player has been changed.
Puzzle Controls each players puzzle.
ServerModel Implements (models) the Server interface.
SetNewPuzzleAll Sets a new puzzle in each of the clients.
StartGameAll Sends a message to the Clients
Stats Figures out game stats
SudokuTimer Keeps track of the elapsed time.
